snippet.title: Scania Truck Driving Simulator The Game - promo trailer
snippet.description: Get behind the wheel of one of the most iconic trucks on the road with this highly detailed Scania R-series simulation! From the developers of the hit title Euro Truck Simulator in cooperation with truck manufacturer SCANIA.
